Output demos/code-search.gif
Set Shell zsh
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 50ms

# Add a codebase
Type "lilbee add ~/projects/lilbee"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 15s

# Search for code with a natural language query
Type 'lilbee search "how does chunking work"'
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 5s
